Its for him you spend all day thinking about. For him you can sit all day and jsut wait for his screen name to come on just so you could say hi. When you sit and stare out your window wondering if he too is there thinking of you. Its for him when at nights you cry silent tears cause you miss him ... the warmth of his touch and the calmness of his voice that soothes you. Its for him that your heart longs and even when people tell you the worse things in the end you still love him in the hours that pass. Your days go on and all that runs through your head is how much you truly just want to stay forever in his arms and let him love you. Just for one night to feel his heart beat against yours. And when you finaly have all your dreams and hopes come true. You will finaly find yourself having something worth loseing in life that you will never want to.

 

Eddy i love you with everything i have and i always will because no1 gives me the things you do and you will always be in my heart no matter what because of you i am who i am now and your brought out the person i've alwyas wanted to be. So thank you for being who you are and loving me even when i was'nt the greatest. Baby you will be in my heart forever. <3

•   Theres always goign to be a point in life were you start to realize who adn what matters to you. But Its then when everything gets defined and you find out wuts real and whats lie's. Theres going to be people who are cold and cruel & then there's goign to be ones who are always there no matter what the cost... those are the ones that you keep close cause you wont find many of them.

 

  •  So now i find myself sitting here alone like a usal feeling. But too the point i jsut dont care. I dont need many friendships i dont need tons of things in this world to make me happy. All i truly need is  people who will be there and someone who loves me for me. And i think ive found that . So it may not be much and to many its probaly stupid but to me thats the greatest thing of all is to be able to at least have a small group of people who truly care about me rather then a huge group who could care less. So think and choose wisely on friendships / b.f or g.f's becuase when it comes down to it are they still going to be there through everything or leave you cold?

 

Dont ask people im jsut so sick of fake people now adays it pisses me off alot. But you cant change the world and thats just how life goes.

 

I Love you Eddy with all my heart and i always will because theres no one out there in this world that could ever make me feel the way you do.

Sometimes i find myself sitting and wondering when my past will be understood. I look apon it quite often even when i should'nt. I know now of how much my happiness erases it but it never completly clears the slate. I wish to let go badly but it never will. The scars remain permant and make my stomach turn in knots when im alone. And you all ask why i fear being alone.... because i fear the things will come back to much and harm me more and i will restart the cycle i was once in. The past is always going to be real the critsim , pain , wounds & mistakes will vaguely live on. But its all due to my own fault for letting them begin in the first place. So one wish i have is that no one ever has to expirence what i have becuase it hurts like hell and effects your everyday life to the worst.

I Love You Eddy
